    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver-focused example of the legendary S54-powered platform. The high-revving 3.2L inline-six delivers linear power through individual throttle bodies, paired with a tactile 6-speed longitudinal manual gearbox. The chassis remains taut, featuring a limited-slip differential that ensures optimal torque vectoring out of apexes. Critical preventative maintenance has been prioritized, including a VANOS system refresh and subframe reinforcement, ensuring the structural integrity matches the mechanical output. While it shows honest patina consistent with an enthusiast-driven vehicle, the compression across all cylinders remains within factory specifications and the throttle response is razor-sharp. A purist\u2019s machine ready for the canyons.",
