    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the legendary S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, delivering linear power delivery up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The chassis remains taut, equipped with Electronic Damper Control and a variable M differential lock for precise cornering. Recent service includes preventative rod bearing replacement and updated throttle actuators, ensuring the valvetrain and induction system operate at peak efficiency. The M-DCT dual-clutch transmission provides lightning-fast gear changes, while the hydraulic steering rack offers the tactile feedback modern EPS systems lack. A well-maintained example of high-revving German engineering.",
